   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>". . . the whole land, and it shall be heard from one end of the land to the other. I (am) Jesus who wrote this epistle with my own hand. The place where this handwriting shall be proclaimed, no power whatever of the adversary, nor the deeds whatever of unclean spirits shall be able to approach nor attain that place for ever. Farewell in peace! Amen."</ab>
         </div>
